     FlexibleContexts
     FlexibleInstances
     FunctionalDependencies
     MultiParamTypeClasses
     OverlappingInstances
     PackageImports
     PatternGuards
     ScopedTypeVariables
     TypeFamilies
     TypeSynonymInstances
     UndecidableInstances

